!!!
html
  head
    title
      block title
      | Chris Wagner's Blog
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1")
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='/stylesheets/style.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', type='text/css', href='//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.1/css/font-awesome.css')'
    link(rel='alternate',type='application/rss+xml',title='RSS',href='/rss')
    | <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    | <script src="js/html5shiv.js"></script>
    | <script src="js/respond.min.js"></script>
    | <![endif]-->
    include includes/mixins
    block head
  body(itemscope,itemtype="http://schema.org/Blog")
    header
      h1
        a(href='/')
          | Chris Wagner's Blog
    .content
      block content
    .sidebar
      aside.bio
        h1
          span.fa.fa-star
          | Bio
        p.avatar
          img(src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3ab6932b729812bc92fee1151dc3b7a2.png")
        p
          | I'm Chris Wagner, a software developer working in <a href="http://www.telerik.com" rel="crush">Telerik</a>'s <a href="http://www.telerik.com/services/overview.aspx">Services Team</a>.
        p
          | As it would happen, my day job and my hobbies intersect very nicely.
